{"tid":1680790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區選參選資格不獲確認　黃之鋒斥選舉主任淪思想警察","createTime":"2019-10-29T04:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T04:55:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b90cb7ef56c47396503ea281f1f472e4b8f491","tid":1680790,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1488784_1_L_20191029122834.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1488784_1_L_20191029122834.jpg&h=777a27da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒被裁定參選區議會提名無效，成為新一屆區議會選舉唯一未能入閘的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n選舉主任蔡亮說，在考慮提名是否有效時，已考慮所有相關因素，指出黃之鋒顯然不會有意圖擁護《基本法》和保證效忠香港特區。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒強烈譴責政府政治篩選，剝奪他的參選權，反映選舉主任淪為思想警察。"},{"pid":"34519e141bfb2702a1b37720e214ddd952a88259","tid":1680790,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c7b1f2ebf0521531e767fbc112f3d68817dfb528","tid":1680790,"uid":243198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"又一奶共機構請777開會!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680169</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急！林奠11.7會去灣仔！<br />\n幫手推呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad5977d70ec79c2ac5474272abe5ffd106a2d263","tid":1680790,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"思想警察 good term"},{"pid":"4934c9b739554ea6d849e37f7aa68505dfd85a90","tid":1680790,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Gphone